content.raw:
The documentation says `This will override an existing local copy of the model.`, so we probably need to change the docs. Also, we may want to do the same change to `DownloadWorld`.

Just a bit more context; this function was implemented this way so there's a path to overriding a model in case that is desired, for example if the user made some local change that broke the model. The responsibility of checking if the model already exists in the cache was kept outside of this function.
